channel.title: How do you make a server?
channel.description:

How do you code?
I'm kind of new to this, I just look at the servers list and visit them. [i]I want to make one of my own.[/i]

I think this might be needed a huge tutorial, and I doubt anyone telling me how to make one... I dont know where else to post this... Help PLEASE
